description:
Take this journey with us as we unpack the different elements of the personality of an entrepreneur. We will tour the Sphere of Mankind, the 9 Hats and other tools and technologies that make of entrepreneurial profile.

You will be guided through developing your Vision, Mission and goals that will set your future into action.

You will also gain an understanding of what roles and activities are required to be a sustainable business creator.
title: Developing an Entrepreneurial Personality
